    schema:activitiesWorkload "100%"@es ;
    schema:courseSchedule <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000442/2025-26/eventSchedule> ;
    schema:description """The course is conceived as an introduction to the field of Design and Construction of Steel-Concrete Composite Structures, reaching medium to advanced level.
No previous knowledge in this kind of structures is required, but it is recommended some basic knowledge about steel and reinforced concrete structures.
Lessons are introduced from the simple basic ideas to more complex concepts, to provide the student with wide enough tools for the analysis of steel-concrete composite structures at the end of the course."""@es ;
