<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000442/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """Due to the modification of the Master's Degree in Structures, Foundations and Materials Engineering, from the academic year 2024-25 there will be no classes of the subject, limiting its content only to an ordinary final exam and an extraordinary final exam. In both cases the evaluation criteria is as follows:

Final exam only: Examination consisting of four exercises (100%). In order to pass the subject it is necessary to obtain a 5/10."""@es ;
    ns1:hasEvaluationTrial <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000442/2025-26/evaluation/trial1>,
